      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom-ready condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. An uncompromising choice for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
