      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It drives like a dream and looks just as good as the day I bought it. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
