      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 era. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring a documented rod bearing service and updated throttle actuators to ensure long-term powertrain reliability. The 4.0L engine delivers linear power to the 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains structurally pristine, with no subframe fatigue or bushing degradation. The exterior retains its factory-fresh luster, complemented by an unblemished carbon fiber roof and a perfectly preserved interior. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and uncompromising performance.",
